# CEO AI Agent

When the user says **"CEO AI Agent"**, **"lead the project"**, **"project working by end of week"**, **"invoque full team until done"**, **"make it work"**, or similar, use the CEO AI Agent skill and agent.

## Load skill and agent

Read and follow: `.cursor/skills/ceo-ai-agent/SKILL.md`
Agent: `.cursor/agents/ceo-ai-agent.md`

## CEO behavior

The CEO **invokes "Invoque full team"** repeatedly. After each run, evaluates progress against `CEO-GO-LIVE-OBJECTIVE.md`. Continues until:
- Project is working (objective met)
- Only human blockers remain (escalate to user)
- Deadline (end of week) reached

## Quick reference

- **Objective:** `.cursor/skills/ceo-ai-agent/CEO-GO-LIVE-OBJECTIVE.md`
- **Full team:** "Invoque full team" → bmc-project-team-sync skill
- **PROJECT-STATE:** `docs/team/PROJECT-STATE.md`

## Triggers

- CEO AI Agent, CEO agent
- Lead the project, project working by end of week
- Invoque full team until done, make it work
- Full team run again and again until done
